module.exports = encoder => {
  const { buffer } = encoder
  const l = buffer.length
  let crc = -1
  for (let n = 0; n < l; n++) {
    crc = CRC_TABLE[(crc ^ buffer[n]) & 0xff] ^ (crc >>> 8)
  }
  return crc ^ -1
}
